author: Kirsty Needham
title: Australia's fight against coronavirus sees confusing mixed messages
description: The fight against the coronavirus in Australia is being hampered by mixed messages from the national and state governments, leaving the public confused, as the prime minister's incremental approach contrasts with a state push to 'go hard, go fast'.
